demos.question: Help predict the numerical value of the topological surface area, TPSA, for a molecule described by the SMILES code, CC(CC1CCCCCN1)NCCC2=CC(=CC=C2)OC,
demos.answer: {"contributor_description":"The molecule contains several functional groups that contribute to the topological polar surface area (TPSA).
